Interface Fixable

All Known Implementing Classes:
AStruct, NParam, Param, SChoice, SParam
public interface Fixable

Allowing for objects to always be of a certain value when picked by the randomizer, ignoring the random choices process., e.g. to make a parameter element.

Felix Dobsaw
